{"tid":1209950,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"其實熱愛去一個地方，行路都行到","createTime":"2019-06-12T12:40:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-12T12:47:13.000Z","uid":88263,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"4875b4c74ad4af14bc00062814004d53e654ca28","tid":1209950,"uid":88263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T12:40:14.000Z","msg":"假如你返工返立法會，你好熱愛返工<br />\n<br />\n假如撞上地鐵全綫訊號故障，地鐵故障又搞到地面大塞車嘅時候，你熱愛返工程度不減<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">你其實可以行路去</span></span>啊哥，我知你唔驚<br />\n<br />\n但啊哥，石禮謙話畀大家知，香港人最緊張嘅係經濟，而<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">每塞6分鐘車，就會有28億損失</span></span><br />\n<br />\n舊Source： <a href=\"https://www.master-insight.com/塞車造成多少經濟損失？/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.master-insight.com%2F%E5%A1%9E%E8%BB%8A%E9%80%A0%E6%88%90%E5%A4%9A%E5%B0%91%E7%B6%93%E6%BF%9F%E6%90%8D%E5%A4%B1%EF%BC%9F%2F&d=NZQUy3Ple5IgpjsjUCCfIh9HEPLFM%2Fpg3GuXTgQF%2FE0%3D&h=40ca62ec\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.master-insight.com/塞車造成多少經濟損失？/</a><br />\n<br />\n大家請守法體驗一流港鐵服務<br />\n[香港命脈][野餐以外]一星期暢遊港鐵體驗包 [鐵膠推介]<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1205357\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1205357</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"a87a16f1e8dc311ac319a69ca2b7891c9743c3a4","tid":1209950,"uid":88263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T12:47:13.000Z","msg":"有手有腳嘅，唔好怕有嘢阻到你去你嘅目的地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n老子表示：千里之行始於足下"}]}